snippet.title: The Jackbox Survey Scramble | Out Now! | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Learn more at https://www.jackboxgames.com/games/the-jackbox-survey-scramble

Discover how people across the country think! The Jackbox Survey Scramble is a collection of hilarious survey-based game modes, using real one-word answers from real people. Really! Grab some friends and start guessing! 

Buy now!
Steam: https://www.jackboxgames.com/games/the-jackbox-survey-scramble
Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/the-jackbox-survey-scramble-switch/
Xbox: https://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/store/the-jackbox-survey-scramble/9N0GR077VG2S
PlayStation: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10011363/
